sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant H as HTTP / RESP3 / gRPC
    participant A as Auth Layer
    participant P as Parser
    participant PL as Planner
    participant E as Engine
    participant G as GraphState
    participant W as WAL
    participant CDC as CDC Bus

    C->>H: Request (JSON / RESP3 / Proto)
    H->>A: Check auth (if enabled)
    A-->>H: Authorized / Denied
    H->>P: Parse command string
    P-->>H: Command enum

    alt Query Command (CONTEXT)
        H->>PL: Plan context query
        PL-->>H: QueryPlan (steps)
        H->>E: execute_command(Command)
        E->>G: RwLock::read()
        G->>G: Vector seed search (HNSW)
        G->>G: Flow score propagation
        G->>G: BM25 text search
        G->>G: Triple-fusion RRF
        G->>G: Budget enforcement (knapsack)
        G-->>E: ContextResult
    else Write Command (NODE.ADD)
        H->>E: execute_command(Command)
        E->>G: RwLock::write()
        G->>G: Add to AdjacencyStore
        G->>G: Set properties
        G->>G: Insert HNSW vector
        G->>G: Index BM25 text
        G-->>E: CommandResponse
        E->>W: WAL append (async)
        E->>CDC: Broadcast GraphEvent
    end

    E-->>H: CommandResponse
    H-->>C: Response (JSON / RESP3 / Proto)
